  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Responsiveness to \"My Projects\" page</li>\n<li>Add UI consistency across Overview and Services pages</li>\n<li>Multiple UI improvements</li>\n<li>Including support for IE11</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Changes the validation error reason on reserved service id error</li>\n<li>Update default metrics interval to 30 days</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Fixed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Create-forwarding port now handles error when installing vpn container</li>\n<li>Fix validation logic on invitation acceptance errors (deleted project, invalid invitation link)</li>\n<li>Display more instructive error on improper image in wedeploy.json</li>\n<li>Display explicit error when including dashes in volume name</li>\n<li>Prioritize CLI metadata for git info on deployments, fixing incorrect branch and commit date on deployments</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>"
      },
